trans-unit.source: Specifies the dimensions of the margins of a printed page.
trans-unit.target: Angir størrelsen på margene i en utskrift.

trans-unit.source: The Margins class is used to manipulate the width of margins in <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController>.
trans-unit.target: Marger klassen brukes til å endre bredden på margene i <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>og <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintController> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings>

trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.MarginsConverter>er typebeskrivelse for denne klassen.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.MarginsConverter>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the bottom margin, in hundredths of an inch.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bunnmargen, hundredeler tomme.

trans-unit.source: If you measure margins in millimeters, multiply the margin width you want in millimeters by 3.937 to determine the correct measurement in hundredths of an inch.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du måler marger i millimeter, multiplikasjon margen ønskede i millimeter av 3.937 å finne riktig målingen hundredeler tomme.

trans-unit.source: For example, if you want a margin of 25mm, multiply by 3.937 and the result is 98 when rounded down.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du vil marger for 25mm, er multiplikasjon av 3.937 og resultatet 98 ved å runde av nedover.

trans-unit.source: You would then set the appropriate <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Margins> member to 98.
trans-unit.target: Deretter setter du riktig <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Margins>medlemmet 98.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.Margins>
